| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2349 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 12272778-7a73-5cb9-aec4-9c17e9b65f45"
